name: DinoSwap
description: DinoSwap, launching on Polygon, is a cross-chain infrastructure platform that builds liquidity for layer-one blockchains, AMMs and partnering projects. The purpose of the DINO token is to facilitate and promote cross chain DeFi liquidity. DINO tokens are a reward for liquidity providers in available farms. DINO itself can be staked/burned in pools to earn different tokens as rewards.
